          "insert": " implements the host-side canvas progression: a static section SVG in the document flow, a top-right expansion action that opens the navigable read-only iframe in a same-window full-screen overlay, and an edit handoff shown only by the doc editor. The Canvas Studio base URL is supplied at build time through "
